Usage: /opt/omi/bin/omiserver.bin [OPTIONS]

This program starts the server.

OPTIONS:
    -h, --help                  Print this help message.
    -d                          Daemonize the server process (POSIX only).
    -s                          Stop the server process (POSIX only).
    -r                          Re-read configuration by the running server (POSIX only).
    --httpport PORT             HTTP protocol listener port.
    --httpsport PORT            HTTPS protocol listener port.
    --idletimeout TIMEOUT       Idle providers unload timeout (in seconds).
    -v, --version               Print version information.
    -l, --logstderr             Send log output to standard error.
    --loglevel LEVEL            Set logging level to one of the following
                                symbols/numbers: fatal/0, error/1, warning/2,
                                info/3, debug/4 (default 2).
